--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHANGES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        o
    ____|____
   |         |  This file lists changes made to the Ansible role.
   |  _   _  |  The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and
   | [_] [_] |  formatted to allow easy grepping by scripts.
   |____~____|
    ___//__//   The fields are:
   /|     |/    B: bug
  //|_____|     F: feature
    _|| ||_     I: improvement
   (__| |__)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.5.2 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.5.1 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.5.0 (2015-05-05)
F: Add basic Portage repository configuration options

* Version 0.4.0 (2015-02-22)
F: Add support for 'http_proxy' option

* Version 0.3.0 (2015-01-29)
F: Add option 'portage_cpu_flags_x86' to define 'CPU_FLAGS_X86' optimizations

* Version 0.2.3 (2014-12-17)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.2.2 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.2.1 (2014-08-22)
I: Ensure Ansible role is OS agnostic

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.1.2 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-07-16)
B: Add missing variable

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-07-09)
F: Initial release
